s://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/288440/', '[1] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[2] Canadian Pharmacists Association "e-CPS.  http://www.pharmacists.ca/function/Subscriptions/ecps.cfm?link=eCPS_quikLink"   (2006):[3] "Product Information. Tasigna (nilotinib)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals  (2007):[4] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0', 1767369485);
